Title: 145: How to Use Data Science In Offline Business
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Serial Entrepreneur, Josey Parks. You will learn how a brick-and-mortar entrepreneur is leveraging data to build a business empire, know how Josey is training his salesmen as data analysts, and get valuable tips on spreading the power of data in the contractor industry.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/145
